quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"ql -ayha alrswl-: awha allah 'ily ann jamaeat min aljini qad aistamaeuu ltlawty llqran, falamaa smewh qaluu lqwmhm: 'iinaa samiena qranana bdyeana fi blaghth wfsahth whkmh wahkamh wakhbarh, yadeu 'iilaa alhaqi walhda, fsddaqna bhdha alquran wemlna bh, walan nushrik birabina aldhy khalaqna ahdana fi ebadth"
  72,2,"ql -ayha alrswl-: awha allah 'ily ann jamaeat min aljini qad aistamaeuu ltlawty llqran, falamaa smewh qaluu lqwmhm: 'iinaa samiena qranana bdyeana fi blaghth wfsahth whkmh wahkamh wakhbarh, yadeu 'iilaa alhaqi walhda, fsddaqna bhdha alquran wemlna bh, walan nushrik birabina aldhy khalaqna ahdana fi ebadth"
  72,3,"wanh tealat ezmt rabana wjlalh, ma atakhadh zawjat wala wldana"
  72,4,"wan sfyhna- wahu 'iblys- kan yaqul ealaa allah taealaa qawlana beydana ean alhaqu walswab, min daewaa alsahbt walwld"
  72,5,"wanna hasibna 'ana ahdana ln yukadhib ealaa allah teala, la min al'iins wala min aljini fi nisbat alsahbt walwld 'ilyh"
  72,6,"wanh kan rijal min al'iins ystjyrwn birijal min aljn, fzad rjal aljnn al'ins basteadhthm bihim khwfana w'irhabana wrebana. whdhh alasteadht bighayr allh, alty neaha allah ela ahl aljahlyt, min alshirk alakbr, aldhy la yghfrh allah 'iilaa baltwbt alnswh mnh. wafi alayat tahdhir shadid min alluju' 'iilaa alsaharat walmshewdhyn washbahhm"
  72,7,wan kafaar al'iins hsbu kama hsbtm- ya maeshar aljn- 'ana allah taealaa lan yabeath ahdana baed almwt
  72,8,"wanna- maeshar aljn- talabna bulugh alsma'; lastmae kalam ahlha, fawajadnaha mulyt bialmalayikat alkathirin aladhin yhrswnha, wbalshhb almahraqat alty yurma biha man yaqtarib mnha"
  72,9,"wana kunaa qabl dhlk natakhidh min alsama' mwade; lnstme 'iilaa akhbarha, faman yuhawil alan astraq alsame yajid lah shhabana balmrsad, yuhrqh wyhlkh. wafi hatayn alaytyn 'ibtal mzaem alsaharat walmshewdhyn, aladhin yddaewn eilm alghyb, wyghrrwn bdeft aleqwl; bkdhbhm waftrayhm"
  72,10,"wanna maeshar aljn- la nelm: ashrrana 'arad allah 'an ynzlh bahl alard, 'am 'arad bihim khyrana whda?"
  72,11,"wana minaa al'abrar almtqwn, waminaa qawm dun dhlk kafaar wfsaq, kunaa frqana wamadhahib mkhtlft"
  72,12,"wana ayqna 'ana allah qadir elyna, wa'anana fi qabdatuh wsltanh, falan nfwth 'iidha 'arad bina amrana 'aynama kna, walan nastatie 'an nuflit min eqabh hrbana 'iilaa alsma', 'iin 'arad bina sw'ana"
  72,13,"w'ina lamaa samiena alquran amnna bh, waqrrna 'anah haqa min eind allh, faman yumin brbh, fa'iinah la yakhshaa nqsanana min hsnath, wala zlmana ylhqh biziadat fi syyath"
  72,14,"wa'anaa minaa alkhadewn lilah baltaet, waminaa aljayrwn alzaalimun aladhin hadu ean tariq alhq, faman 'aslam wakhadae lilah baltaet, fawlyk aladhin qsdu tariq alhaqu walswab, wajthdu fi aikhtiarih fhdahm allah 'ilyh, wa'amaa aljayrwn ean tariq al'islam fakanuu waqwdana ljhnm"
  72,15,"wana minaa alkhadewn lilah baltaet, waminaa aljayrwn alzaalimun aladhin hadu ean tariq alhq, faman 'aslam wakhadae lilah baltaet, fawlyk aladhin qsdu tariq alhaqu walswab, wajthdu fi aikhtiarih fhdahm allah 'ilyh, wa'amaa aljayrwn ean tariq al'islam fakanuu waqwdana ljhnm"
  72,16,"wanh law sar alkufaar min al'iins waljinu ealaa tariqat al'islam, walam yhydu eanha lanzlna ealayhim ma'an kthyrana, wlwssaena ealayhim alrizq fi aldnya; lnkhtbrhm: kayf yashkurun nem allah elyhm? waman yuerd ean taeat rabih wastmae alquran wtdbrh, waleamal bih yudkhilh edhabana shdydana shaqqana"
  72,17,"wanh law sar alkufaar min al'iins waljinu ealaa tariqat al'islam, walam yhydu eanha lanzlna ealayhim ma'an kthyrana, wlwssaena ealayhim alrizq fi aldnya; lnkhtbrhm: kayf yashkurun nem allah elyhm? waman yuerd ean taeat rabih wastmae alquran wtdbrh, waleamal bih yudkhilh edhabana shdydana shaqqana"
  72,18,"wan almasajid lebadt allah whdh, fala taebuduu fiha ghyrh, wa'akhlasuu lah alduea' walebadt fyha; fa'iina almasajid lm tubn 'iilaa lyuebad allh wahdah fyha, dun min swah, wafi hdha wjwb tnzyh almasajid min kl ma yshwb al'iikhlas llh, wamutabaeat rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  72,19,"wanh lamaa qam muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, yaebud rbh, kad aljini yakunun ealayh jamaeat mtrakmt, baeduha fawq bed; min shdt azdhamhm lsmae alquran mnh"